author: Giorgio Mendoza
description: This month, Shuttle Computers launched the SPCNV03, an ultra-compact edge computer based on the NVIDIA Jetson Orin Nano. It delivers up to 40 TOPS of AI performance in a fanless aluminum chassis and carries EMC, Safety, and RoHS certifications for use in robotics, automation, video analytics, and smart city applications. title: Shuttle Fanless Mini Edge PC with Up to 40 TOPS AI Performance
